ele repair in the era of ART. Reprod Med Biol. 2024;23(1):e12589.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"2. Lima TF et al. Effect of microsurgical varicocelectomy on semen parameters and testosterone. BJUI Compass. 2020;1(3):93-99.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"3. Takeshima T et al. Oxidative stress and male infertility. Reprod Med Biol. 2020;20(1):41-52.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"4. Birowo P et al. Varicocele treatment and pregnancy rates: systematic review and meta-analysis. Andrology. 2023.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"133","text":"5. Agarwal A et al. Male infertility. Lancet. 2020;397(10271):319-333.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"133","text":"6. DynaMed. Varicocele Management & Evaluation. EBSCO Information Services. 2024.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"133","text":"7. AUA/ASRM Guidelines on Male Infertility. 2021.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"133","text":"8. EAU Guidelines on Sexual and Reproductive Health. 2024.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":141,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Varicocele iPad","id":"map_891","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Varicocele iPad"}